'''Carleton Hoffner''' is an [[United States|American]] [[figure skater]] who competed in both [[ice dance]] and pairs with partner [[Anne Davies (figure skater)|Anne Davies]]. They won the dance title at the 1946 [[U.S. Figure Skating Championships]] and won the bronze medal in pairs at the 1949 [[World Figure Skating Championships]].<ref>{{PDFlink|1=[http://www.isu.org/vsite/vfile/page/fileurl/0,11040,4844-148238-165454-56217-0-file,00.pdf ISU: World Figure Skating Championships Medalists ]}}</ref>
